snippet.title: Centipede PS1 Game Intro Movie HD
snippet.description:
Opening movie of the PS1 game Centipede, a good action game based on the classic arcade game.

Intro del juego de PS1 Centipede, un buen juego de acción basado en el clásico arcade.

Game copyright: Hasbro Interactive (1999)

More information about the game here:
http://www.psxdatacenter.com
